The paper discusses the software engineering process of game development, which is a subfield of software engineering (cs.SE). It also mentions the multidisciplinary nature of game development, which involves sound, art, control systems, AI, and human factors, indicating a possible connection to graphics (cs.GR), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and cybernetics (cs.CY).
